    "href": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Game_Awards"
  }), "Game Awards"), " als \xABTrending Gamer of the Year\xBB nominiert."), mdx("p", null, "2016 war auch das Gr\xFCndungsjahr des Youtube-Channels Noclip, mit folgendem Versprechen:"), mdx("blockquote", null, mdx("p", {
    parentName: "blockquote"
  }, "\xABGamers deserve our media that reflects our passions, a press that uses its access to tell stories about how games get made, the people who play them, and the ways in which they reflect our lives\u2014stories that make us proud to be gamers.\xBB", "\u202F", mdx("sup", _extends({
