  }, "Plus: "), "Your name in the credits, Monthly Live Q&A, Early Access, Behind-the-Scenes Video Library, Bonus Scenes, Bonus Podcasts, Discord Access, Patron Posts, our love and thanks!\xBB", mdx("sup", _extends({
